articleBody:
Technology is touching new dimensions every day in the country and the world. With this growing technology, internet freedom is under attack in many countries around the world. This is to say of Google CEO Sundar Pichai. Pichai said in an interview with the BBC that many countries are obstructing the flow of information. Apart from this, he also told which two things will emerge as a revolution in the coming time. Let us know what these are.
'Revolution will come from artificial intelligence
According to Google CEO Sundar Pichai, artificial intelligence and quantum computing will bring revolution in the coming 25 years. Now what are these two, let's also know about it. Regarding artificial intelligence, Pichai said, "I see it as the best technology made by humans. Whatever you think about fire, electricity or the Internet, Exactly it's going to happen. I think maybe even better than that." Artificial intelligence system is designed to work like humans, especially it is used to solve a particular type of problems.&nbsp;
'Quantum computing will bring change'
According to Sundar Pichai, quantum computing is a completely different concept. This is based on common computing binaries 0 or 1, these are called bits. Quantum computers work on qubits. This makes a possible for substances to be in multiple states at the same time. Pichai said that it is not so easy to understand this but in the coming time, it can bring a big revolution in the world. However, many technology experts, including Pichai, believe that it will not work everywhere.&nbsp;
